<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body class="bg-gray-50 flex flex-col min-h-screen font-sans text-gray-900">

    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>

        <main class="flex-grow max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 w-full">

            <div class="mb-12 border-b border-gray-200 pb-6 text-center md:text-left">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-black mb-4 tracking-tight">
                    Sertifikasi & Pelatihan</h1>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-2xl">
                    Dokumentasi pengembangan diri, pencapaian akademis, dan pelatihan profesional
                    yang telah saya selesaikan untuk terus meningkatkan kompetensi.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">

                <div
                    class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden flex flex-col sm:flex-row group">
                    <div
                        class="sm:w-2/5 h-48 sm:h-auto bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center p-4 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-gray-200">
                        <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-black transition-colors duration-300"
                            fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5"
                                d="M9 12l2 2 4-4M7.835 4.697a3.42 3.42 0 001.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 014.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 001.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 013.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010 4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806 1.946 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138 3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-4.438 0 3.42 3.42 0 00-1.946-.806 3.42 3.42 0 01-3.138-3.138 3.42 3.42 0 00-.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 010-4.438 3.42 3.42 0 00.806-1.946 3.42 3.42 0 013.138-3.138z">
                            </path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 sm:w-3/5 flex flex-col justify-center">
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">
                            Tahun 2026</p>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Pelatihan Dasar (Latsar)
                            CPNS</h2>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
                            Pendidikan dan pelatihan pembentukan karakter serta kompetensi teknis,
                            termasuk perancangan aktualisasi sistem digital E-Perjadin.
                        </p>
                        <a href="#"
                            class="text-black text-sm font-semibold hover:underline inline-flex items-center">
                            Lihat Kredensial <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14">
                                </path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div
                    class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 border border-gray-200 overflow-hidden flex flex-col sm:flex-row group">
                    <div
                        class="sm:w-2/5 h-48 sm:h-auto bg-gray-100 flex items-center justify-center p-4 border-b sm:border-b-0 sm:border-r border-gray-200">
                        <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-gray-400 group-hover:text-black transition-colors duration-300"
                            fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5"
                                d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z">
                            </path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="p-6 sm:w-3/5 flex flex-col justify-center">
                        <p class="text-xs font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">
                            Tahun 2025</p>
                        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Advanced Data Processing &
                            Programming</h2>
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-4">
                            Sertifikasi penyelesaian pelatihan pemrograman Python, integrasi GUI
                            dengan Tkinter, dan otomasi pengolahan data menggunakan Microsoft Excel
                            tingkat lanjut.
                        </p>
                        <a href="#"
                            class="text-black text-sm font-semibold hover:underline inline-flex items-center">
                            Lihat Kredensial <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1" fill="none"
                                stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"
                                    stroke-width="2"
                                    d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14">
                                </path>
                            </svg>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </main>

        <%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>

</html>